<h2>Join as TrackerPeer</h2>

<p>When you become a TrackerPeer whatever updates sent to the site will also be relayed to your site. Please note
that when you join you are essentially asking a request and the current site owner has to accept you as a 
TrackerPeer before sending your site updates.</p>

<%= form_for :tracker_peer, :url => { :action => 'create' } do |f| %>
<p>
  <%= f.label :name %>
  <br>
  <%= f.text_field :name %>
</p>

<p>
  <%= f.label :url %>
  <br>
  <%= f.text_field :url %>
</p>

<p>
  <%= f.label :callback_url %>
  <br>
  <%= f.text_field :callback_url %>
</p>

<p>
  <%= f.label :admin_email %>
  <br>
  <%= f.text_field :admin_email %>
</p>

<p>
  <%= submit_tag 'Request' %>
<p>

<% end %>
